  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"article-viewer markdown-body result\">\n   <div style=\"height:0;font-size:0;\">\n    <svg width=\"0\" height=\"0\" viewBox=\"0 0 171 48\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n     <clipPath id=\"jcode-logo-clip\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M29.6735 30.7507L4.24023 7.29975L10.1773 0.857178L29.6735 18.8468L49.2491 0.857178L55.1762 7.29975L29.6735 30.7507ZM59.4204 47.1347H0V23.8225H8.7619V38.3827H50.6684V23.8225H59.4204V47.1347ZM166.243 18.8667C165.88 18.6445 165.49 18.3891 165.067 18.1129C164.925 18.0195 164.778 17.9237 164.628 17.826C164.043 17.4295 163.438 17.0132 162.814 16.5672C162.189 16.1212 161.585 15.6553 160.98 15.1697C160.376 14.684 159.801 14.1983 159.266 13.7127C158.205 14.7038 157.055 15.6553 155.806 16.5573C154.557 17.4593 153.378 18.2324 152.268 18.8766H147.609C148.402 18.4603 149.225 17.9648 150.087 17.3998C150.95 16.8348 151.782 16.2699 152.565 15.6851C153.358 15.1102 154.062 14.5551 154.696 14.0397C155.331 13.5243 155.806 13.0882 156.143 12.7512H162.259C162.626 13.0882 163.141 13.5144 163.805 14.0397C164.469 14.5651 165.193 15.1102 165.996 15.6752C166.788 16.25 167.611 16.815 168.464 17.3899C169.316 17.9648 170.109 18.4603 170.842 18.8766H166.233L166.243 18.8667ZM151.971 33.1692C151.852 32.8124 151.713 32.416 151.554 31.9699C151.439 31.6447 151.318 31.3195 151.195 30.9905C151.15 30.8682 151.104 30.7455 151.059 30.6219C150.89 30.166 150.722 29.7299 150.553 29.3136C150.517 29.2238 150.481 29.1358 150.447 29.0498C150.321 28.7375 150.206 28.4522 150.097 28.2035H153.071C153.102 28.2757 153.135 28.3515 153.17 28.4306L153.17 28.4317C153.278 28.678 153.399 28.9569 153.527 29.264C153.643 29.5444 153.759 29.8294 153.879 30.1224C153.932 30.2542 153.987 30.3876 154.042 30.5228C154.22 30.9589 154.389 31.405 154.557 31.8708C154.726 32.3367 154.875 32.7629 155.013 33.1692H157.729V27.1033H149.393V24.8633H157.729V22.0979H148.789V19.7786H169.633V22.0979H160.723V24.8633H169.028V27.1033H160.723V33.1692H163.518C163.706 32.8025 163.884 32.3961 164.073 31.9501C164.261 31.5041 164.429 31.0581 164.598 30.6021C164.766 30.1462 164.925 29.7101 165.064 29.2938C165.203 28.8775 165.322 28.5108 165.401 28.2134H168.345C168.077 29.0559 167.78 29.9182 167.453 30.8202C167.125 31.7221 166.818 32.5052 166.531 33.1692H170.456V35.5877H147.946V33.1692H151.951H151.971ZM125.131 12.7712V16.5773H122.841V18.966H125.131V24.7544L122.742 25.359V27.9063L125.131 27.3017V29.3931C125.131 30.0473 125.101 30.6519 125.042 31.2168C124.982 31.7818 124.893 32.3071 124.754 32.8027C124.615 33.2983 124.447 33.774 124.249 34.23C124.051 34.6859 123.803 35.1319 123.495 35.5879H126.618C127.004 34.8049 127.282 33.9029 127.47 32.8721C127.658 31.8413 127.748 30.6816 127.748 29.3931V26.6277L129.809 26.0727V23.5254L127.748 24.0804V18.966H129.839V16.5773H127.748V12.7712H125.131ZM129.879 33.5956C129.7 34.339 129.482 35.0031 129.234 35.5879H129.244H132.01C132.416 34.3588 132.703 32.9216 132.882 31.2565C133.06 29.5913 133.149 27.8568 133.149 26.0429V19.9275H145.004V13.1776H130.681V26.0231C130.681 26.9152 130.652 27.7973 130.592 28.6794C130.533 29.5616 130.444 30.414 130.325 31.2466C130.206 32.0692 130.057 32.8622 129.879 33.5956ZM142.456 17.8658H133.239V15.269H142.456V17.8658ZM138.601 33.4271H136.381V28.6993H134.269V35.5978H145.143V28.6993H143.002V33.4271H140.732V27.49H144.855V21.4241H142.793V25.4284H140.732V20.9186H138.591V25.4284H136.529V21.4241H134.468V27.49H138.601V33.4271ZM106.326 32.9906V12.7808H109.25V19.2233H119.519V21.8202H109.25V33.0005H120.302V35.5478H97.4453V33.0005H106.326V32.9906ZM72.3125 24.9129C72.7486 23.5748 73.1352 22.1971 73.4623 20.7797C73.7893 19.3722 74.0669 17.9251 74.3047 16.4483H72.4116V14.129H81.2033V16.4483H76.743C76.6538 17.0826 76.5646 17.717 76.4655 18.3513C76.3664 18.9857 76.2474 19.6101 76.1087 20.2544H81.0645V34.656H73.8686V24.9129H72.3125ZM76.188 32.416H78.7848V22.5241H76.188V32.416ZM89.6083 35.5877L89.6171 35.5778H92.9783C93.3351 34.8939 93.6226 34.0316 93.8604 33.0008C94.0983 31.97 94.2173 30.8499 94.2173 29.6407V22.99H92.7107L93.3153 13.3459H82.1845V15.7347H90.5896L90.0345 22.99H85.4554L85.7527 17.0727H83.1856L82.8089 25.3589H91.6204V29.5416C91.6204 30.8202 91.4321 31.9799 91.0455 33.0404C90.661 34.0954 90.1784 34.9445 89.6171 35.5778H89.6083V35.5877ZM90.5103 28.3621V30.7013H82.2043V28.3621H90.5103Z\"></path>\n     </clipPath>\n    </svg>\n   </div>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/9456ab9014694573909de2733acc5b69~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5YmN56uv5Lmd5ZOl:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1764654719&amp;x-signature=w4sPNHGfhJ%2Bv0Xhu3jDr%2BmOaPz0%3D\" alt=\"test.gif\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p><strong>设计小姐姐</strong>： “搞一下这样的<strong>回弹</strong>效果，你行不行？”\n     <br>\n     <strong>我</strong>：“行！直接梭哈 50 行 keyframes + transform + 各种百分比，搞定 ”\n     <br>\n     <strong>设计小姐姐</strong>：“太硬（撇嘴），不够 Q 弹（鄙视）”\n     <br>\n     <strong>我</strong>：(裂开)\n     <br>\n     <strong>隔壁老王</strong>：这么简单你都不行，我来一行贝塞尔 cubic-bezier(0.3, 1.15, 0.33, 1.57) 秒了😎\n     <br>\n     <strong>设计小姐姐</strong>：哇哦！（兴奋）好帅！（星星眼🌟）好Q弹！（一脸崇拜😍）\n     <br>\n     <strong>我</strong>：<strong>“？？？”</strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <hr>\n   <h3 data-id=\"heading-1\">1️⃣ cubic-bezier 是什么？</h3>\n   <p>在 CSS 动画里，我们经常写：</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-css code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"css\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-attribute\">transition</span>: all <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.5s</span> ease;</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p>但其实 <code>ease</code>、<code>linear</code>、<code>ease-in-out</code> 这些都只是封装好的贝塞尔曲线。\n    <br>\n    底层原理是：</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-css code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"css\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\">cubic-bezier(x1, y1, x2, y2)</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p>这四个参数定义了<strong>时间函数曲线</strong>，控制动画速度的变化。</p>\n   <ul>\n    <li><code>x</code>：时间轴（必须在 0～1 之间）</li>\n    <li><code>y</code>：数值轴（可以超出 0～1！）</li>\n   </ul>\n   <p>👉 当 y 超过 1 或小于 0 时，动画值就会<strong>冲过终点再回弹</strong>，\n    <br>\n    这就是“回弹感”的核心。</p>\n   <hr>\n   <h3 data-id=\"heading-2\">2️⃣ 回弹的本质：过冲 + 衰减</h3>\n   <p>想象一个球掉下来：</p>\n   <ul>\n    <li><strong>过冲</strong>：球落地时会压扁（超出终点）</li>\n    <li><strong>回弹</strong>：然后反弹回来，再逐渐稳定</li>\n   </ul>\n   <p>在动画中，这个“过冲”就是 y&gt;1 的部分，\n    <br>\n    而“回弹”就是曲线回到 y=1 的过程。</p>\n   <hr>\n   <h2 data-id=\"heading-3\">🧪 二、一行贝塞尔的魔法</h2>\n   <h3 data-id=\"heading-4\">✅ 火箭发射</h3>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/d945616e56f74171afda7e6b38b97c8c~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5YmN56uv5Lmd5ZOl:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1764654719&amp;x-signature=lUyE6LGLXrjzlCGpwDn2f6gf%2F8M%3D\" alt=\"export_1764044056566.gif\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-html code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"html\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"bounce\"</span>&gt;</span>🚀发射！<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">style</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"css\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.bounce</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\"> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">transition</span>: transform <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.8s</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">cubic-bezier</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0.68</span>, -<span class=\"hljs-number\">0.55</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.27</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">1.55</span>);</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.bounce</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:hover</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\"> <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">transform</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">translateY</span>(-<span class=\"hljs-number\">500px</span>);</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\">}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">style</span>&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p><span href=\"https://code.juejin.cn/pen/7576535022065647654\" class=\"code-editor-container\"><iframe class=\"code-editor-frame\" data-code=\"code-editor-element\" data-code-id=\"7576535022065647654\" data-src=\"https://code.juejin.cn/pen/7576535022065647654\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://code.juejin.cn/pen/7576535022065647654\"></iframe><span class=\"loading-placeholder\" style=\"display: none;\"><img class=\"placeholder-image\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAADwAAAA8CAYAAAA6/NlyAAAAJElEQVRoge3BMQEAAADCoPVP7WkJoAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAbjh8AAFte11jAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC\" loading=\"lazy\"><span class=\"loading-logo\"></span></span></span> 💡 <strong>参数解析：</strong></p>\n   <ul>\n    <li>y1 = -0.55 → 先轻微反向缩小</li>\n    <li>y2 = 1.55 → 再冲过头 55%，最后回弹到原位</li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 data-id=\"heading-5\">🧩 四、常用贝塞尔参数</h2>\n   <table>\n    <thead>\n     <tr>\n      <th>效果描述</th>\n      <th>贝塞尔参数</th>\n      <th>备注</th>\n     </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n     <tr>\n      <td>微回弹（按钮）</td>\n      <td><code>cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.31, 0.7, 1)</code></td>\n      <td>轻柔弹性</td>\n     </tr>\n     <tr>\n      <td>强回弹（卡片）</td>\n      <td><code>cubic-bezier(0.68, -0.55, 0.27, 1.55)</code></td>\n      <td>爆发力强</td>\n     </tr>\n     <tr>\n      <td>柔和出入</td>\n      <td><code>cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1.4)</code></td>\n      <td>iOS 风</td>\n     </tr>\n     <tr>\n      <td>弹性放大</td>\n      <td><code>cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275)</code></td>\n      <td>弹簧感</td>\n     </tr>\n     <tr>\n      <td>火箭猛冲</td>\n      <td><code>cubic-bezier(0.68, -0.55, 0.27, 1.55)</code></td>\n      <td>推背感</td>\n     </tr>\n    </tbody>\n   </table>\n   <hr>\n   <h2 data-id=\"heading-6\">🧰 五、调试神器推荐</h2>\n   <ul>\n    <li>\n     <p>🎨 <a href=\"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fcubic-bezier.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://cubic-bezier.com\" ref=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">cubic-bezier.com</a>\n      <br>\n      拖动手柄实时预览动画，复制参数一键搞定。</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p>⚙️ <a href=\"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Feasings.net\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://easings.net\" ref=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">easings.net</a>\n      <br>\n      收录各种 easing 函数（含物理弹簧、阻尼等）。</p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文深入浅出地讲解了如何利用 CSS `cubic-bezier` 曲线参数，特别是超出 0-1 范围的 y 值，为前端动画实现生动自然的“Q 弹”回弹效果。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文深入浅出地讲解了如何利用 CSS `cubic-bezier` 曲线参数，特别是超出 0-1 范围的 y 值，为前端动画实现生动自然的“Q 弹”回弹效果。",
  "summary": "文章以一个生动的 UI 设计需求场景开篇，引入了 CSS 动画中 `cubic-bezier` 时间函数的核心概念。作者详细解释了 `cubic-bezier(x1， y1， x2， y2)` 四个参数的含义，并着重指出当 y 轴参数超出 0 到 1 的范围时，动画会产生“冲过终点再回弹”的关键效果。文章进一步阐述了回弹效果的本质是“过冲 + 衰减”，通过形象地比喻球落地反弹的过程，帮助读者理解动画的物理特性。此外，文章提供了“火箭发射”等实际代码示例，展示了如何一行代码实现复杂的弹性动画，并汇总了多种常用贝塞尔参数及其对应的效果描述。最后，文章推荐了 `cubic-bezier.com` 和 `easings.net` 等实用调试工具，极大提升了文章的实践指导价值和可操作性。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "`cubic-bezier` 曲线 y 轴参数超出 0-1 范围是实现动画回弹的关键。",
      "explanation": "通过将 `cubic-bezier` 的 y1 或 y2 参数设置在 0 或 1 之外，可以使动画在到达终点前或后产生短暂的“过冲”效果，这是模拟物体弹性回弹感的核心机制。"
    },
    {
      "point": "动画回弹效果的本质是“过冲”与“衰减”的结合。",
      "explanation": "回弹动画通过先短暂超越目标状态（过冲），随后逐渐平稳地回到目标状态（衰减），从而在视觉上模拟出真实世界中物体富有弹性的运动轨迹。"
    },
    {
      "point": "利用在线调试工具可高效生成并优化 `cubic-bezier` 参数。",
      "explanation": "`cubic-bezier.com` 和 `easings.net` 等工具提供直观的图形化界面，允许开发者实时拖拽控制点并预览动画效果，极大地简化了复杂弹性动画曲线的调试与参数选择过程。"
    }
  ],
